rComments: My combustion engines professor at METU. Learnt a lot from him including not to exaggerate your answers even if they're correct. Can't believe he's still around.

Top combustion scientist in Canada and I think one of the best in the world. It is amazing how he can cover the very practical aspects related to industry as well as very fundamental problems of reacting flows. And at the end he ties the two together. One of the best professors at UTIAS.
He is the best in his field in Canada, without doubt.
Professor Gulder is knowledgeable.  His lecture notes is extremely helpful even in my later Engineering career.  However, his teaching style is a little bit dull.
